1
00:00:09,114 --> 00:00:13,160
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

2
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:17,800
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

3
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:22,840
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

4
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:28,000
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

5
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,415
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

6
00:00:32,415 --> 00:00:37,167
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

7
00:00:37,167 --> 00:00:42,400
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

8
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:47,853
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

9
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:55,760
=Rise Again=

10
00:00:56,144 --> 00:00:58,878
=Episode 16=

11
00:01:26,799 --> 00:01:28,200
This can't be...

12
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:38,920
Grandpa, look at Wubing.

13
00:01:40,239 --> 00:01:41,159
Interesting.

14
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:43,599
Those who step onto those steps

15
00:01:44,079 --> 00:01:46,359
will have their spiritual power sealed
for a time.

16
00:01:47,719 --> 00:01:51,599
Every step feels
like carrying a heavy weight.

17
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:54,280
Low-level cultivators

18
00:01:54,519 --> 00:01:57,760
can barely manage two or three steps.

19
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:58,120
is Wubing

20
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,319
going to be okay?

21
00:02:01,439 --> 00:02:02,120
Look at him.

22
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:03,799
He's reached the summit.

23
00:02:04,719 --> 00:02:05,959
So he's one of us after all.

24
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:07,519
My apologies. Please enter.

25
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:08,560
How is that possible?

26
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:10,080
He's reached the top,

27
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:12,159
so he qualifies
to attend the tournament.

28
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:17,840
There's something wrong
with the steps.

29
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:20,199
Are you questioning the tournament?

30
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:22,400
If you have a problem, you can leave.

31
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:24,280
Come here.

32
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:47,919
Useless.

33
00:02:51,599 --> 00:02:52,599
(Su Wubing,)

34
00:02:53,199 --> 00:02:55,039
(today I will make sure you die here.)

35
00:02:56,080 --> 00:02:57,360
I told you he is amazing!

36
00:02:58,680 --> 00:02:59,879
Don't get too excited yet.

37
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:01,599
Pulling the sword

38
00:03:02,159 --> 00:03:03,520
will be the real test.

39
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:05,840
For all these years,

40
00:03:06,199 --> 00:03:07,879
no one has ever been able
to move that sword.

41
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:10,319
If he can pull it out,

42
00:03:11,879 --> 00:03:13,159
then I can rest assured

43
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:15,159
and leave you in his care.

44
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:29,400
Everyone comes here

45
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:33,280
to witness the rebirth
of this divine sword.

46
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,840
But throughout history,

47
00:03:36,639 --> 00:03:38,680
no one has ever been able to draw it.

48
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:39,879
Of course.

49
00:03:40,520 --> 00:03:42,719
If anyone can even make it budge,

50
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:47,000
they are a rare genius.

51
00:03:47,479 --> 00:03:51,520
And the Two Realms Mountain will ensure
the Fan City's cultivation world

52
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:53,639
returns to its peak!

53
00:03:55,159 --> 00:03:56,280
Even if we can't pull it out,

54
00:03:57,080 --> 00:03:58,400
just touching the divine sword

55
00:03:59,199 --> 00:03:59,840
is worth it.

56
00:04:00,879 --> 00:04:01,479
Everyone.

57
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:04,080
The divine sword may appear blunt,

58
00:04:04,919 --> 00:04:06,560
but its edge remains.

59
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,759
Don't get yourselves hurt.

60
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:11,759
Don't go.

61
00:04:12,879 --> 00:04:14,199
You were already lucky

62
00:04:14,199 --> 00:04:15,159
to make it up here.

63
00:04:15,639 --> 00:04:16,480
I brought you here

64
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:17,560
to broaden your horizons.

65
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:19,839
I'm here today

66
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:23,759
only to take back what belongs to me.

67
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:27,319
How arrogant.

68
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:29,000
You think passing a staircase

69
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,040
makes you invincible?

70
00:04:30,759 --> 00:04:32,920
Why not just say
the whole city belongs to you?

71
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:35,240
Mr. Gu,

72
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:37,120
he doesn't know any better.

73
00:04:37,759 --> 00:04:38,560
Su Wubing,

74
00:04:38,959 --> 00:04:41,079
I suggest you take a good look here,

75
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:43,240
then go back and brag all you want.

76
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:45,959
What's all this barking?

77
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:48,240
As expected of the Gu family.

78
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:49,600
They even bring watchdogs when out.

79
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:50,439
You!

80
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:56,319
Who goes first?

81
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:57,920
Me.

82
00:04:59,120 --> 00:05:00,160
I'll try.

83
00:05:17,199 --> 00:05:18,160
How is this happening?

84
00:05:20,399 --> 00:05:21,959
I warned you all.

85
00:05:23,279 --> 00:05:24,759
The sword chooses its master.

86
00:05:25,639 --> 00:05:28,800
Force it, and you'll only hurt yourself.

87
00:05:30,639 --> 00:05:31,360
Count me in!

88
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:33,240
I don't believe I can't pull it out.

89
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:56,839
"Chooses its master"? Please.

90
00:05:57,079 --> 00:05:58,120
Just a normal sword.

91
00:05:58,319 --> 00:05:59,160
Let me try.

92
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:10,279
Isn't it just a sword?

93
00:06:10,279 --> 00:06:11,160
What's so hard about it?

94
00:06:11,399 --> 00:06:11,959
I'll do it.

95
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:13,560
Why is there only you?

96
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:16,240
My father is busy elsewhere.

97
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:18,759
Having me is enough.

98
00:06:19,319 --> 00:06:22,160
I heard your father once failed here.

99
00:06:23,759 --> 00:06:24,920
I just want to try.

100
00:06:47,199 --> 00:06:48,279
Why is it so heavy...?

101
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:51,480
A bunch of overestimating fools.

102
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:53,240
I'll do it.

103
00:06:55,199 --> 00:06:56,000
Su Wubing,

104
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:57,759
aren't you impressive?

105
00:06:57,879 --> 00:06:59,279
Dare to bet with me

106
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:01,319
on who can draw the sword?

107
00:07:02,519 --> 00:07:03,560
I'm not interested in that.

108
00:07:03,879 --> 00:07:04,560
I already said it.

109
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,759
I'm only here to take back what's mine.

110
00:07:08,079 --> 00:07:08,879
Scared, huh?

111
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,560
After I pull it out,

112
00:07:10,879 --> 00:07:12,519
you'll be the first I kill.

113
00:07:27,319 --> 00:07:28,199
It's Mr. Gu!

114
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:31,279
Mr. Gu is resonating with the sword?

115
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,680
See that?

116
00:07:40,439 --> 00:07:42,319
Mr. Gu is number one in Fan City.

117
00:07:46,079 --> 00:07:48,199
The divine sword
has chosen me as its master.

118
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:49,800
From this day on,

119
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:52,000
Fan City is mine to run.

120
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:53,800
Su Wubing.

121
00:07:54,160 --> 00:07:55,360
I'll kill you right here.

122
00:08:05,879 --> 00:08:06,560
Mr. Gu.

123
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:12,720
Mr. Gu.

124
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:17,040
Who?!

125
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:18,720
Who dares ruin my good time?

126
00:08:19,759 --> 00:08:21,399
Touching the divine sword for a moment,

127
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:22,759
you should be satisfied.

128
00:08:24,519 --> 00:08:25,800
Save the sarcasm.

129
00:08:26,439 --> 00:08:27,600
Mr. Gu, he...

130
00:08:31,199 --> 00:08:32,000
Su Wubing.

131
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:34,759
Dare to make a bet with me?

132
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:36,720
If you can pull it out,

133
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:39,159
I'll kneel and apologize in public.

134
00:08:39,799 --> 00:08:40,960
If you can't,

135
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:42,440
you'll take your own life.

136
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:44,080
Do you dare?

137
00:08:44,519 --> 00:08:45,759
I've said it before.

138
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:47,120
I came today

139
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:49,279
only to take back what's mine.

140
00:08:49,759 --> 00:08:50,960
Nothing I wouldn't dare do.

141
00:08:51,799 --> 00:08:52,200
Don't go.

142
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:54,360
So many just failed.

143
00:08:54,639 --> 00:08:55,240
It's too dangerous.

144
00:08:56,039 --> 00:08:56,519
Don't worry.

145
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:59,240
Mind your manners, junior.

146
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:01,159
Every blade of grass

147
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:04,159
belongs to me
in the Two Realms Mountain.

148
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:07,200
Even if the sword finds no master,

149
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:09,360
it's not yours.

150
00:09:24,879 --> 00:09:26,679
(Heavenly God Sword has slept
for ten thousand years.)

151
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:29,600
(With my power alone,)

152
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:31,120
(I still can't awaken it.)

153
00:09:35,039 --> 00:09:35,720
Su Wubing.

154
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:36,679
You also...

155
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:41,480
This...?

156
00:09:42,679 --> 00:09:43,480
How is that possible?

157
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:44,759
Ningxue.

158
00:09:45,519 --> 00:09:46,360
I need your help.

159
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:50,759
What do I do?

160
00:09:51,799 --> 00:09:52,440
Without you,

161
00:09:52,639 --> 00:09:53,679
it won't wake up.

162
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:12,440
(Su Wubing.)

163
00:10:13,399 --> 00:10:15,240
(Could you really be its master?)

164
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:18,559
The sky I failed to split
in my past life...

165
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:21,279
want to help me try again in this one?

166
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:28,120
How is it a broken sword?

167
00:10:30,919 --> 00:10:31,559
Su Wubing.

168
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:35,080
You went through all that trouble
for a piece of scrap metal?

169
00:10:37,799 --> 00:10:38,480
A broken sword?

170
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:42,320
Where is the Heavenly God Sword?

171
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:44,840
Sword, come!

172
00:11:26,542 --> 00:11:30,645
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

173
00:11:30,645 --> 00:11:35,365
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

174
00:11:35,365 --> 00:11:40,245
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

175
00:11:40,245 --> 00:11:45,365
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

176
00:11:45,365 --> 00:11:49,765
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

177
00:11:49,765 --> 00:11:54,445
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

178
00:11:54,445 --> 00:11:59,845
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

179
00:11:59,845 --> 00:12:06,239
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪
